# 🌐 2️⃣ REST vs WebSocket

This is a favorite interview question.

---

## REST

Best when:

* request → response
* data changes occasionally

Examples:

* login
* fetching profile
* product details

---

## WebSocket

Best when:

* updates happen continuously
* real-time communication needed

Examples:

* WhatsApp
* online games
* stock prices

---

### Mental Model

REST = Email 📧

WebSocket = Phone Call 📞

---

### Comparison

| REST             | WebSocket             |
| ---------------- | --------------------- |
| Request-response | Persistent connection |
| Simpler          | Real-time             |
| Stateless        | Stateful              |

---

### Interview Gold Line ⭐

👉 Use REST for normal operations and WebSockets for real-time updates.

